            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Naruto <span class="text-muted">Did you ever seen it? I think you do.</span></h2>
            <p class="lead">
                Naruto is a hyperactive and knuckle-headed ninja still living in Konohagakure. Shunned because of the Kyuubi inside him, Naruto struggles to find his place in the village, while his burning desire to become the Hokage of Konohagakure
