            <img class="bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="https://i1.sndcdn.com/artworks-000490379475-k6atd7-t500x500.jpg" width="500" height="500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="Placeholder: 500x500"
